title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Beastmaster 2
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Beastmaster 2
description:
This week on Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe dive into “Beastmaster 2: Through the Portal of Time,” a 1991 sequel full of loincloths, green magic, animal hijinks and a lethal dose of goofy one-liners.
